<task>
Scan the document below across the 4 pillars (Background / Materials / Framework / Intent).
Emit 4-12 findings total. Intent failures are ALWAYS BLOCKER (CSW gate).

Each finding MUST include:
- pillar: one of "Background"|"Materials"|"Framework"|"Intent"
- severity: "BLOCKER"|"IMPROVEMENT"|"NICE-TO-HAVE"
- issue: 1-line problem (≤60 chars)
- suggest: action verb + concrete replacement text (NEVER "更完整" / "更清晰")
- anchor: { line_range: [start,end], snippet: ≤120 char raw quote }

Use the 6 challenge dimensions (data integrity / logical consistency / feasibility /
stakeholders / risk / ROI) as the lens for HOW to challenge inside each pillar.

Return JSON ONLY:
{
  "findings": [
    {"id":"p1","pillar":"...","severity":"...","issue":"...","suggest":"...",
     "anchor":{"line_range":[1,3],"snippet":"..."}}
  ]
}
</task>

